{"tid":1474233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（有圖，求fact check）麗港城疑似有人臉識別CCTV","createTime":"2019-08-15T05:55:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T07:15:38.000Z","uid":41771,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1816a1c93dd10442207b5ce92639b5b477d0ff1e","tid":1474233,"uid":41771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:55:16.000Z","msg":"小弟係麗港城返工（但我唔係住係麗港城），行過見到有<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">疑似</span></span>係人臉識別嘅閉路電視，想請住係麗港城或對CCTV有認識嘅巴絲解答。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>如果我誤會左請各位不吝賜教，小弟願意道歉。</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dRrMsM4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdRrMsM4.jpg&h=4f90fa1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8LWwDTN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8LWwDTN.jpg&h=f1045586&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ce7scdR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fce7scdR.jpg&h=9df3077e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z6D7cdV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ6D7cdV.jpg&h=9d3cd0a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"266357d7035ff7fffd9475bdee17770b0945b8ef","tid":1474233,"uid":257422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:55:43.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">818 手足要絕對和平！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n依兩日trump/國際社會已經開哂口，關鍵時刻，咪掛住衝搞到外國幫唔到你口呀！！！<br />\n<br />\n就算出老解，你反抗都唔會有用，之前都傾好左，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">出老解係全人類返屋企！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n行前面既手足<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住幫幫手適當時拉住d激動手足</span></span>，唔洗理佢係咪鬼，總之睇撚住大家要冷静！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地主動出手既話外國點樣幫你口？？？？<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">你要贏老共緊係要引美帝打佢，自己掉磚邊會掉得贏；依家就係關鍵時刻